teen-agers plunged 300 feet off a road in the San Gabriel Mountains
early Wednesday, critically injuring four youths, authorities said.
   Three others had moderate injuries and the driver suffered minor
injuries, said Deputy Dan Cox of the Los Angeles County Sheriff's
