to be near his family.
   Flowers, 48, fell ill Friday night while performing in a
showroom at the Harrah's gambling resort in Lake Tahoe, publicist
JoAnne Geffen said.
   ``He was hospitalized in Lake Tahoe and today he is being moved
to an undisclosed hospital near his family in Georgia,'' she said.
