<HEAD>Troops In Sealed-Off Town Launch Helicopter Search for Arabs</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: INSERTS one graf after 3rd graf pvs, Except for ... UPDATING
with 200 residents in custody. Picks up 4th graf pvs, ``We have ...
SUBBING 21st graf pvs, The suspect ... to CORRECT name to
