reducing upward pressure on inflation and interest rates.
   Recent weakness in oil prices kept the pressure on energy
issues. Atlantic Richfield dropped 1[ to 80[; Mobil \ to 42{; Amoco
1[ to 73[; Exxon | to 46, and Schlumberger 1\ to 31\.
